resolution: Duplicate; superseded by pm-github-9dqy
expected_result: single feature
actual_result: closed as duplicate
close_reason: "Duplicate of pm-github-9dqy (a failed JSON-parse on the create response masked a successful create, so the feature was created twice). 9dqy is the canonical feature carrying all child tasks/decisions."
